title: How do I roll back a commit on my project?

sections.title: Symptoms
content: • I recently committed a change and would like to remove it.

sections.title: Cause
content: You made a recent change to your build, but would like to now remove it or roll it back.

sections.title: Resolution
content: At this time, we unfortunately do not have a feature for rolling back commits. This feature is in development however and we expect to have it in a later Unity version preview build.
The build will be available here once it is ready.
